WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:13.310
You are permitted to speak in your own behalf.

00:00:13.310 --> 00:00:19.429
Concerning all the things of which I am accused by the Jews, King Agrippa, I consider

00:00:19.429 --> 00:00:27.629
myself happy that it is before you, I am to make my defense this day, especially because

00:00:27.629 --> 00:00:34.630
you are an expert on all the customs, as well as the controversies among the Jews.

00:00:34.630 --> 00:00:35.630
Number 4, I beg you.
